###ENVIRONMENT VARAIBLES
SetEnv LOWCAL_ENV local

###BASIC CONFIG
Options -Indexes +FollowSymLinks
ServerSignature Off
IndexIgnore *
RewriteEngine on

###HTACCESS PROTECTION
<Files ~ "^.*\.([Hh][Tt][Aa])">
order allow,deny
deny from all
satisfy all
</Files>

##CATCHALL FOR ROUTING
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteRule .* bootstrap.php [NC]